{
  "stem": "1249.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I feel so embarrassed, because I'm so-- It's OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where was your brother at this time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was he still with you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took him before they took us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went with this-- I don't know how you call that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- like a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the labor camp, we found out later he went to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As, as remember, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I remember, I only-- if not, I, I don't know about that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know that when we walked or woke up, we heard this-- how you call that?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shooting, but with the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not rifle, this is the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Machine guns, thank you, machine guns over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And probably nobody asked them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, unfortunately, Hungarians were not too good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't say everybody was bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure you found a few nice people who hidden people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, unfortunately, over there, more they killed, they were happier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were big, very much against the, the, the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very big anti, antisemite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So at the end of your few weeks in this ghetto, what happened?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to a, a-- we went to the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they-- before they took us the labor camp, they took us like in a stable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's sad to tell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 17 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one by one, girls and women was taken [SOBS] in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SOBS] They examined us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Do you understand what I mean?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understand what you mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who examined you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a general.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the woman I know where is I come from.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in a-- professional call girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and she was--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
